  </p>

  <h3>How long does initial setup take?</h3>

  <p>
    A basic AI OS with context, memory, and one skill takes about 2-3 hours. A full system with multiple skills and automation takes a weekend. We have a step-by-step guide for the <a href="/blog/how-to-build-an-ai-os-in-a-weekend">weekend build approach</a>.
